org.testah.framework.report.jira

Class BasicJiraRemoteLinkBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.testah.framework.report.jira.AbstractJiraRemoteLinkBuilder
      • org.testah.framework.report.jira.BasicJiraRemoteLinkBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JiraRemoteLinkBuilder

    public class BasicJiraRemoteLinkBuilder
extends AbstractJiraRemoteLinkBuilder
    The type Basic jira remote link builder. This is a basic implimentation of JiraRemoteLinkBuilder to make it easier to have Jira integration out of the box. This class needs to be instantiated and set into the global TS.getTestPlanReporter() at runtime. Best to do this in a setup common to all testplans.

    Example: TS.getTestPlanReporter().setJiraRemoteLinkBuilder(new BasicJiraRemoteLinkBuilder(defaultIcon, defaultIcon)); .
